  "prompt": "Can we eat Apple at night?",
  "response": "Yes, you can eat apples at night. Apples are a healthy snack that can provide various benefits due to their high fiber content, vitamins, and antioxidants. Eating apples at night can satisfy your hunger without adding many calories, and the fiber can aid in digestion.\n\nHowever, it\u2019s important to consider individual preferences and digestive systems. Some people might find that eating fruits late at night can cause discomfort or disrupt sleep, so it's best to listen to your body and see what works best for you. Generally, moderate consumption should not cause problems for most people.",
